title: Add low-volume mode for rooms
updated_at: "2026-07-14T04:07:05Z"
---
Allow rooms to opt into a low-volume presentation mode that hides or suppresses most operational detail, including tool execution updates and cron prompts, while retaining important user-facing results and alerts.